---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---
<Layout title="Privacy Policy | RevAgentic" description="Privacy Policy for RevAgentic (Agentic Revenue Lab LLC).">
<nav class="border-b border-brand-border bg-white px-6 py-4"><div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto"><span class="font-display font-bold text-brand-navy">revagentic<span class="text-brand-purple">.ai</span></span></div></nav>
<main class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 py-16">
<h1 class="font-display font-bold text-4xl text-brand-navy mb-4">Privacy Policy</h1>
<p class="text-brand-muted text-sm mb-12">Last updated: May 3, 2026</p>
<section class="mb-10"><h2 class="font-display font-semibold text-2xl text-brand-navy mb-4">Who We Are</h2><p class="text-brand-muted font-body leading-relaxed">This Privacy Policy applies to Agentic Revenue Lab LLC, operating as RevAgentic, reachable at hello@revagentic.ai.</p></section>
<section class="mb-10"><h2 class="font-display font-semibold text-2xl text-brand-navy mb-4">Information We Collect</h2><p class="text-brand-muted font-body leading-relaxed">We collect information you provide directly, including name, email address, phone number, and business details when you submit a form on revagentic.ai. We also collect standard usage data through analytics tools.</p></section>
<section class="mb-10"><h2 class="font-display font-semibold text-2xl text-brand-navy mb-4">How We Use Your Information</h2><p class="text-brand-muted font-body leading-relaxed">We use your information to deliver the Revenue Systems Diagnostic and related services, communicate with you about your inquiry, and send SMS and email follow-ups you have consented to.</p></section>
<section class="mb-10"><h2 class="font-display font-semibold text-2xl text-brand-navy mb-4">SMS Messaging</h2><p class="text-brand-muted font-body leading-relaxed">If you provide your phone number and consent to SMS, we will send messages related to your diagnostic and services. Reply STOP to opt out at any time. We do not sell your phone number to third parties.</p></section>
<section class="mb-10"><h2 class="font-display font-semibold text-2xl text-brand-navy mb-4">Data Sharing</h2><p class="text-brand-muted font-body leading-relaxed">We do not sell your personal information. We may share data with service providers who help us operate our business, under confidentiality agreements.</p></section>
<section class="mb-10"><h2 class="font-display font-semibold text-2xl text-brand-navy mb-4">Contact</h2><p class="text-brand-muted font-body leading-relaxed">Questions? Email <a href="mailto:hello@revagentic.ai" class="text-brand-purple hover:underline">hello@revagentic.ai</a>.</p></section>
<div class="border-t border-brand-border pt-8"><p class="text-brand-muted font-body text-sm">Agentic Revenue Lab LLC d/b/a RevAgentic · Chicago, IL</p></div>
</main>
<footer class="border-t border-brand-border px-6 py-8 bg-white mt-16"><div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-brand-muted text-sm"><p>© 2026 RevAgentic. All rights reserved. RevAgentic is a service of Agentic Revenue Lab LLC.</p></div></footer>
</Layout>